00:28:13.780 --> 00:28:17.050
Can we come up with a
mathematical formulation of

00:28:17.050 --> 00:28:18.490
the shape of that curve?

00:28:18.490 --> 00:28:21.660
And we can, and here's
the central

00:28:21.660 --> 00:28:25.540
tenet kinetic of theory.

00:28:25.540 --> 00:28:36.640
Kinetic theory says that the
reaction rate can be expressed

00:28:36.640 --> 00:28:38.187
