00:28:57.970 --> 00:29:00.570
So that's the overall idea.

00:29:00.570 --> 00:29:06.250
So now let's say that the rate
of change, the instant rate of

00:29:06.250 --> 00:29:14.190
change of concentration ci, is
proportional to the instant

00:29:14.190 --> 00:29:16.410
