00:30:05.160 --> 00:30:06.580
This is order reaction.

00:30:06.580 --> 00:30:08.060
It's not mole number
over there.

00:30:08.060 --> 00:30:10.300
You've got to be pluralistic
today.

00:30:10.300 --> 00:30:11.730
n is going to be used
in different ways.

00:30:11.730 --> 00:30:18.510
So this is called order
of reaction.

00:30:18.510 --> 00:30:19.825
And there's a constant.

00:30:19.825 --> 00:30:20.480
See up there?

00:30:20.480 --> 00:30:21.850
It's a proportionality.

